{"tid":2310073,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是靚午 臘味飯 配 沙嗲金錢肚","createTime":"2020-12-03T04:02:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-03T08:31:51.000Z","uid":33359,"like":38,"dislike":87,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"aa0176a4cdd7fad060c15e0278b89fb77b45cb34","tid":2310073,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T04:02:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nrvBzQp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnrvBzQp.jpg&h=a511f270&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/snV6cB7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsnV6cB7.jpg&h=6180448d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bAgw8av.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbAgw8av.jpg&h=89c6bab9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ewYoeQy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FewYoeQy.jpg&h=19413d99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢啲天氣最岩食啲臘味飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講吓味道先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n臘肉肥瘦分明<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咬落去油脂香同玫瑰露既香氣爆哂出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n臘腸口感軟熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n肥膏都好夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食到我差啲中風<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n金錢肚口感軟糯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n沙嗲汁味入哂去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最正係底個啲南瓜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入口即化得黎索哂沙嗲汁同金錢肚既味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食落個膽囊好c伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我仲開咗個講觀塘美食既mewe gp<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n誠邀大家一齊入黎分享觀塘美食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://mewe.com/join/觀塘飲食台1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmewe.com%2Fjoin%2F%E8%A7%80%E5%A1%98%E9%A3%B2%E9%A3%9F%E5%8F%B01&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPWXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=b3e8edea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mewe.com/join/觀塘飲食台1</a>"},{"pid":"bafc47aa8979a984c24d198282f38eb3152b54ae","tid":2310073,"uid":211578,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T04:02:53.000Z","msg":"觀塘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1676a9cdbfadcf5e1b9fb0a70a6c5e3cc4eea783","tid":2310073,"uid":899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T04:02:55.000Z","msg":"臘味師"},{"pid":"587011168c2a4c44df982386e84dc95dc0175c95","tid":2310073,"uid":364608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T04:03:02.000Z","msg":"Fat fat<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14c3b8cc50ee150994cf9628a8848cd82f898bf1","tid":2310073,"uid":157826,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T04:03:04.000Z","msg":"早食師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2e55f3e377507b8d4d4f8ae1367985a93a89de9","tid":2310073,"uid":117037,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T04:03:14.000Z","msg":"d飯好唔惦"},{"pid":"85d9a82e87e7f38d5aa53fb9dbc3a0de4d131000","tid":2310073,"uid":301749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T04:03:16.000Z","msg":"分享師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8377d6ee57c313f96695efb504e59e80e1c60719","tid":2310073,"uid":372210,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T04:03:29.000Z","msg":"貼定先。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6LjVQJ5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6LjVQJ5.gif&h=ca66b83a&s={SI